node.text:
Here’s what we’ve been working on  since the beginning of the pandemic early last year.

We’re so excited to announce Noma Projects and the launch of Project 001, noma’s line of garums, coming later this year. This is the culmination of 18 years of knowledge, craft and experimentation channeled into a new endeavor. To bring Project 001 to life, we collaborated with design agency @gretelnyc and one of our long-time favorite artists, @davidshrigley . For first access to preorders and news on upcoming projects, visit the link in bio! 

Music: @stefanpasborg / Ibrahim Electric
DOP: Mathias Nyholm Schmidt 
Editor: Rasmus Nyholm Schmidt

node.text:
We've just received news that noma has been awarded three Michelin stars. 

This is one of the highest mountains to scale in the restaurant world. My first thoughts when I heard the news were of all the people who have passed through noma over the past 18 years: the hundreds of cooks and servers, stages and dishwashers that were essential pieces in this crazy puzzle we've put together. 

And, of course, this news is a direct reflection of our extraordinary team working today. Some of the hungriest, most talented, most dedicated badass humans I've ever had the pleasure of knowing. We just wrapped up our summer season, so the team is scattered across the world, enjoying their well-earned time off, but I want you all to know how special you truly are. Please enjoy this moment, wherever you may be. We fucking did it!!

As much as I love these three stars, the only star that we really need is the one we wake up to every morning. It will feel much brighter for me and the whole noma family tomorrow. In these strange and challenging times, we should all bask in whatever light we can find.

node.text: A dark caramel, butterscotch fudge with the texture of ice cream. A traditional recipe would hold serious amounts of salted butter, here we’ve replaced butter with reindeer bone marrow fat. It’s an unusual sweet bite, that never the less works quite well with your coffee after dinner. Are you game?
